@baseUrl = http://localhost:5111

### ===========================
### Authors
### ===========================

### List all authors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search authors by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors?search=orwell&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get author details (George Orwell)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1

### Get author details (Yuval Noah Harari)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/5

### Create a new author
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Gabriel",
  "lastName": "Garcia Marquez",
  "biography": "Colombian novelist and Nobel Prize winner, author of One Hundred Years of Solitude.",
  "birthDate": "1927-03-06",
  "country": "Colombia"
}

### Update an author
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "George",
  "lastName": "Orwell",
  "biography": "English novelist, essayist, journalist and critic. Best known for 1984 and Animal Farm.",
  "birthDate": "1903-06-25",
  "country": "United Kingdom"
}

### Delete an author (will fail — author has books)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1

### ===========================
### Categories
### ===========================

### List all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get category details (Fiction)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1

### Create a new category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Philosophy",
  "description": "Books about philosophical thought and inquiry."
}

### Update a category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fiction",
  "description": "Novels and stories based on imagined events and characters."
}

### Delete a category (will fail — category has books)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1

### ===========================
### Books
### ===========================

### List all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search books by title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?search=1984&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search books by author name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?search=asimov&page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter books by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?category=Science Fiction&page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter available books only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?available=true&page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter unavailable books only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?available=false&page=1&pageSize=10

### Sort books by year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?sortBy=year&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get book details (1984)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1

### Get book details (I, Robot — 0 available copies)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/5

### Create a new book
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Brave New World",
  "isbn": "9780060850524",
  "publisher": "Harper Perennial",
  "publicationYear": 1932,
  "description": "A dystopian novel about a futuristic World State.",
  "pageCount": 288,
  "language": "English",
  "totalCopies": 3,
  "authorIds": [1],
  "categoryIds": [1, 2]
}

### Update a book
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "1984",
  "isbn": "9780451524935",
  "publisher": "Signet Classics",
  "publicationYear": 1949,
  "description": "A dystopian novel set in a totalitarian society ruled by Big Brother.",
  "pageCount": 328,
  "language": "English",
  "totalCopies": 4,
  "authorIds": [1],
  "categoryIds": [1, 6]
}

### Delete a book (will fail — book has active loans)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1

### Get loan history for a book (1984)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1/loans?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get active reservations for a book (I, Robot)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/5/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10

### ===========================
### Patrons
### ===========================

### List all patrons
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search patrons by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons?search=alice&page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter patrons by membership type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons?membershipType=Premium&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron details (Alice Johnson — Premium)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1

### Get patron details (Frank Davis — Inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/6

### Create a new patron
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Grace",
  "lastName": "Lee",
  "email": "grace.lee@email.com",
  "phone": "555-0107",
  "address": "111 Willow Way",
  "membershipType": "Student"
}

### Update a patron
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@email.com",
  "phone": "555-0101",
  "address": "123 Maple St, Apt 4B",
  "membershipType": "Premium"
}

### Deactivate a patron (will fail if patron has active loans)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1

### Get patron's loans (Alice — all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1/loans?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's active loans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1/loans?status=Active&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's fines (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/5/fines?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's unpaid fines
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/5/fines?status=Unpaid&page=1&pageSize=10

### ===========================
### Loans
### ===========================

### List all loans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?page=1&pageSize=10

### List active loans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?status=Active&page=1&pageSize=10

### List overdue loans via filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?overdue=true&page=1&pageSize=10

### List loans in a date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?fromDate=2025-01-01&toDate=2025-12-31&page=1&pageSize=20

### Get loan details (Loan 1 — Alice has 1984)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/1

### Check out a book (Bob checks out Pride and Prejudice)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 3,
  "patronId": 2
}

### Return a book (Loan 2 — Bob returns Animal Farm)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/2/return

### Renew a loan (Loan 1 — Alice renews 1984)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/1/renew

### Get all overdue loans (also flags them)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/overdue?page=1&pageSize=10

### ===========================
### Business Rule Tests — Loans
### ===========================

### DENIED: Check out a book for inactive patron (Frank, id=6)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 3,
  "patronId": 6
}

### DENIED: Check out a book with no available copies (I, Robot)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 5,
  "patronId": 1
}

### DENIED: Renew an overdue loan (Loan 8 is overdue)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/8/renew

### ===========================
### Reservations
### ===========================

### List all reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10

### List pending reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations?status=Pending&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get reservation details (Reservation 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/1

### Get reservation details (Reservation 3 — Ready)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/3

### Create a reservation (Eva reserves I, Robot)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 5,
  "patronId": 5
}

### DENIED: Reserve a book patron already has on active loan (Carol has I, Robot loan 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 5,
  "patronId": 3
}

### Cancel a reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/1/cancel

### Fulfill a "Ready" reservation (Reservation 3 — Eva picks up Foundation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/3/fulfill

### ===========================
### Fines
### ===========================

### List all fines
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines?page=1&pageSize=10

### List unpaid fines
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines?status=Unpaid&page=1&pageSize=10

### List paid fines
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines?status=Paid&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get fine details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines/1

### Pay a fine
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/fines/1/pay

### Waive a fine
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/fines/3/waive
